<item>
            <title>[SOLR-847] Enhance the snappull command in ReplicationHandler to take in masterUrl</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-847</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;It should be possible to pass in the masterUrl as a parameter to snappull command so that we can replicate data from arbitrary master&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12408257">SOLR-847</key>
            <summary>Enhance the snappull command in ReplicationHandler to take in masterUrl</summary>
